long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
# Play more games on the top-left menu.

🔼 Dive into the iconic world of Geometry Dash with the original Chrome extension – Geometry Dash Original! 🎶✨ Experience the pulse-pounding rhythm, electrifying obstacles, and adrenaline-pumping challenges right in your browser. 🕹️🔥 Immerse yourself in the timeless gameplay that has captivated millions around the globe. Jump, fly, and flip your way through an ever-evolving geometric landscape. 🚀📐 Install Geometry Dash Original now and relive the excitement of the classic game directly from your Chrome browser. Get ready to test your skills, conquer levels, and unlock the full potential of this legendary gaming experience! 🌐🎮
